descr: My first day with the glasses is coming to an end. It hasn't bothered me too much, and people around me seem also not to care about the weird device in the glasses. Now I'm preparing to sleep, filling the required logs. I'm a little worried about my studies and assignments that are due soon
Now I arrived to the university. People are looking more at me, but not as much as I expected. It seems they are more discreet here than in my country.
